Date: Mon, 10 Mar 2025 18:14:07 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 11/11] wifi: ath12k: Rename ath12k_* to ath12k_wifi7*

Rename functions and global defines from ath12k_* to ath12k_wifi7_* to
align with the movement of code from ath12k/ to ath12k/wifi7 directory.

Tested-on: QCN9274 hw2.0 PCI WLAN.WBE.1.3.1-00173-QCAHKSWPL_SILICONZ-1
Tested-on: WCN7850 hw2.0 PCI WLAN.HMT.1.0.c5-00481-QCAHMTSWPL_V1.0_V2.0_SILICONZ-3
Tested-on: RDP441 WLAN.WBE.1.3.1-00130-QCAHKSWPL_SILICONZ-1

Signed-off-by: Kiran Venkatappa <quic_kiranv@quicinc.com>
